rec_search.title: Mafteaḥ leshon ha-ḳodesh that is The key of the holy tongue : wherein is conteineid, first the Hebrue grammar (in a manner) woord for woord out of P. Martinius. Secondly, a practize upon the first, the twentie fift, and the syxtie eyght Psalmes, according to the rules of the same grammar. Thirdly, a short dictionary conteining the Hebrue woords that are found in the Bible with their proper significations. All Englished for the benefit of those that (being ignoraunt in the Latin) are desirous to learn the holy tongue; by Iohn Udall.
